headline: Corpay Named the Official Foreign Exchange Provider of Major League Soccer
summary: TORONTO, May 29, 2025--Corpay, Inc.*, (NYSE: CPAY) a global leader in corporate payments, is pleased to announce that Corpay’s Cross-Border business has entered into a multi-year agreement with Major League Soccer (MLS) to become the league’s Official Foreign Exchange (FX) Provider.
